{"tid":525689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【東鐵跪低●大圍】隧道內死火列車焗爆 于先生：停咗一粒鐘","createTime":"2018-01-11T02:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T03:22:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"11d964cd7a324f1c9df579f35f655f91faf9498d","tid":525689,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180111/large/1515636844_cdf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180111%2Flarge%2F1515636844_cdf5.jpg&h=fc62714a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上9時15分許，港鐵東鐵綫疑發生訊號故障，全線服務暫停，港鐵正安排免費接駁巴士，接載受影響乘客。<br />\n<br />\n讀者于先生於今早10時許報料稱，他乘搭的列車由大圍開往九龍塘，1個小時前已在途中的隧道內死火，之前在大圍站已經有問題，進入隧道才表示需要搶修，目前車廂「迫到沙甸魚咁，想走都走唔到，空氣亦開始侷促」，有乘客亦疑身體不適蹲下，要由其他乘客讓座與他休息。于先生稱，暫時仍未見有港鐵職員安排他們離開車廂，但據悉列車將倒後駛回大圍站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180111/57692856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F57692856&d=rAtfao6yB4dxNkpNzqY3kO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=b0258f18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F57692856&h=1f1d3587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180111/57692856</a>"},{"pid":"c918a40a9f068d5bd748c9a5df0faf023b5bb990","tid":525689,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"多謝支那同民賤聯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有佢地擋住<br />\n市民吹得漲？"},{"pid":"a6f265639b2610e87ed0eb6ca98a146674e85bec","tid":525689,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:56:46.000Z","msg":"用強國野唔爆炸已經要還神啦"},{"pid":"202575d3b15e64df0b56e978f6ee81913db545e5","tid":525689,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p